Job Details
Our company is on the hire for diligent and motivated SALES AND LEASING CONSULTANTS.
We are one of the leading and very active real estate companies in Dubai (as we are an Authorised Agent for EMAAR) and still strengthening our position in the industry.
We want you to become part of us if;
-          you are hard working and has a drive for a successful career
-          can communicate in English (written and verbal)
-          have Strong Sales Skills
-          familiar with Dubai addresses
If you are the person we’ve been looking for, then WE WOULD LIKE YOU to join our team!!!
What we offer;
-          Residence visa
-          Full back office support (including drafting of Agreements)
-          Marketing in every property specialised marketing channel
-          Basic salary for the first 3 months (will not be deducted from any commission earned)
-          A very pleasant and joyful work environment
If interested, kindly send your CV now.
Email: derick@uniqueproperties.ae
**Only emails with SALES AND LEASING CONSULTANT as the Subject Line will be considered**
